                      <div align="left">
                      <table border="0" width="696" height="136">
                        <tr><td width='686' height='19' valign='top' align='left'> <font face='Arial,sans-serif' SIZE=2 COLOR=#ffff80> 2000-08-23 - Guild Event on Erollisi Marr</font> </td></tr><tr><td width='686' height='19'></td></tr><tr><td width='686' height='19' valign='top' align='left'> <font face='Arial,sans-serif' SIZE=2 COLOR=#C0C0C0> <p><font face="verdana" size="2" color="#C0C0C0">On Friday, August 25 8:00pm
EST, a major RP campaign between the <a href="http://www.shadowguard.org/">Shadow
Guard</a> and <a href="http://www.holystorm.org/">Knights of the Holy Storm</a>
of the Erollisi Marr server will begin with a special Fight Night in the Arena
of Lake Rathe. These two longstanding roleplaying guilds will begin a campaign
involving the fabled Tears of Tunare, and the Shadow Guards theft of this sacred
potion from the protection of the Holy Storm. The campaign, which has the
potential of evolving into a Guild War, will begin in the Arena through a series
of 3 on 3 duels. These duels are open to any in attendance between levels 20-48.
A prize of 900pp will go to the 1st placed team and 300pp to the 2nd place team.
Rules and structure of the contest are available on the &quot;War Room
(Inter-guild events) board on the <a href="http://pub5.ezboard.com/fshadow52488thewarroominterguildevents.showMessage?topicID=29.topic">Shadow
Guard message board</a>.</font>
<p><font face="verdana" size="2" color="#C0C0C0">You may sign up your team of 3,
or feel free to come and be matched with those in attendance. There will also be
the opportunity to wager on the teams in attendance!</font>
<p><font face="verdana" size="2" color="#C0C0C0">Ninnin D Arksoul<br>
High Magus of the Spurned<br>
Inter-Guild Relations<br>
Shadow Guard</font></p>
<font face="verdana" size="2" color="#C0C0C0"><br>
